headline: 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks You Can Buy With $130 Now and Hold at Least a Decade
summary: From the end of 2023 through Nov. 12, the benchmark S&P 500 index climbed 25% higher.  Most dividend payers offer uninspiring yields, but Brookfield Infrastructure (NYSE: BIPC)(NYSE: BIP), Realty Income (NYSE: O), and Royalty Pharma (NASDAQ: RPRX) provide yields above 3% at recent prices, and you don't need to be rich to take advantage of them.  Brookfield Infrastructure Corp. (BIPC) shares offer a 3.8% dividend yield.
